snippet.title: SteamWorld Dig 2 – Release Date Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
SteamWorld Dig 2 premieres on Nintendo Switch on September 21, with the PS4 and Steam versions coming a few days after. Official website: http://imageform.se/game/steamworld-dig-2/
